{"number":100,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" وَٱلْعَـٰدِيَـٰتِ ضَبْحًا","translation":"By the racers, panting,","transliteration":"WalAAadiyati dabha","page":599},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"فَٱلْمُورِيَـٰتِ قَدْحًا","translation":"And the producers of sparks [when] striking","transliteration":"Falmooriyati qadha","page":599},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"فَٱلْمُغِيرَٰتِ صُبْحًا","translation":"And the chargers at dawn,","transliteration":"Falmugheerati subha","page":599},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"فَأَثَرْنَ بِهِۦ نَقْعًا","translation":"Stirring up thereby [clouds of] dust,","transliteration":"Faatharna bihi naqAAa","page":599},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"فَوَسَطْنَ بِهِۦ جَمْعًا","translation":"Arriving thereby in the center collectively,","transliteration":"Fawasatna bihi jamAAa","page":599},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ لِرَبِّهِۦ لَكَنُودٌ","translation":"Indeed mankind, to his Lord, is ungrateful.","transliteration":"Inna al-insana lirabbihi lakanood","page":599},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ لَشَهِيدٌ","translation":"And indeed, he is to that a witness.","transliteration":"Wa-innahu AAala thalikalashaheed","page":599},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لِحُبِّ ٱلْخَيْرِ لَشَدِيدٌ","translation":"And indeed he is, in love of wealth, intense.","transliteration":"Wa-innahu lihubbi alkhayri lashadeed","page":599},{"numberInSurah":9,"arabic":"۞ أَفَلَا يَعْلَمُ إِذَا بُعْثِرَ مَا فِى ٱلْقُبُورِ","translation":"But does he not know that when the contents of the graves are scattered","transliteration":"Afala yaAAlamu itha buAAthira mafee alquboor","page":599},{"numberInSurah":10,"arabic":"وَحُصِّلَ مَا فِى ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"And that within the breasts is obtained,","transliteration":"Wahussila ma fee assudoor","page":600},{"numberInSurah":11,"arabic":"إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ لَّخَبِيرٌۢ","translation":"Indeed, their Lord with them, that Day, is [fully] Aware.","transliteration":"Inna rabbahum bihim yawma-ithinlakhabeer","page":600}]}